lead_paragraph: West Indies were dismissed for 330 just before lunch on the fifth and final day of the weather-ravaged third test against Australia at the Sydney Cricket Ground (SCG) on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: West Indies Dismissed for 330 at Lunch in Sydney
